comments.commentBody:
@Fun Bobby

I like your idea of adding spinach to the sauce!  I added the al dente pasta to the sauce with a little pasta water to finish cooking and it absorbed the flavors into the pasta for a more flavorful dish.  Also topped with extra grated cheese. 
We enjoyed it immensely and will make it again.

@Dana
Thank you for using the recipe. I have been surfing the comments and very few (you are the first) have made the recipe, itself. How can I know whether it is worth making when it is full of substitutions, some not even Asian? 
I am all for changing recipes AFTER having eaten the actual one. How do I know I like it if “it” isn’t even there?

@Brie
Many of us Migraine sufferers cannot deal with MSG. Instant aura and bad headache!
The re-introduction into foods is a Nightmare.
